    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AppController
    Act as a Controller for the entire Application
    Controller
    Controller interface
    DeviceName
    representation of the available devices on the application will be expanded once functionalities are added
    HomeController
    Home Controller Class for the Main Application Page
    HomeModel
    Home Model Class - Model Class for the main Home Page
    HomePageStates
    States ENUM for the Home Page
    HomeView
    View of the Main Home Page called post successful authentication
    HttpRequestQuery
    HTTP Request Query Builder Class creates the GET request for the application to interface with the REST API
    LoginController
    Login Controller Class utilizes method calls to handle activities on the Login Page of the application relies on the AppController Class for navigating to home page after successful login
    LoginModel
    Login Model for handling primarily authentication
    LoginView
    GUI View Class for the Login Page
    MockHomeModel
    mock model for testing Controller - utilized for testing
    MockHttpRequestQuery
    mock class for the HttpRequestQuery
    MockLoginModel
    Mock class for the LoginModel to aid in the testing of the LoginController class
    Model
    Model Interface due to differences in data handling in the login and main page there are no strict requirements here - however, will likely need to refactor for future iterations
    OuraRing
    Oura Ring Class extending the Wearables Abstract
    SPEAKER
    SPEAKER - defines roles for the chat interface USER inputs or questions will appear on the left side of the chat interface AI inputs and responses will appear on the right side of the chat interface
    View
    View Interface
    Wearables
    Interface for all Wearable Devices
    WearablesAbstract
    Abstract class of Parent Class Wearables contains methods that are shared across the Wearable Sub-classes
